1.Elastic Block Store:        [Change-what you need at particular time]
  * server creation:
    create 2-servers(ap-south-1a) normal way, 2-volumes created automatically after server creation.

  * volume creation:
    volumes --> create volume --> volume type(General purpose SSD(gp2) --> size(1) --> avilability zone(ap-south-1a) --> snapshort id(Dont create volume from snapshot)
    --> create volume.
    Actions --> attach volume --> instance(attch server-1) --> device name(xvde) --> attach volume.

  * connect mstsc:  [Do both servers]
    Administrator & password 
    server-1 --> click on windows symbol(server manager) --> disk management --> file storage and services --> volumes --> new volumes(mouse right click)
    --> next --> dick --> 2-next --> drive letter(D) --> next --> create. [check loacl once]

2.EFS:
  * setup:
    create file system --> custom --> name(efs-1) --> life cycle management --> enhanced --> elastic --> next
    --> mount target(select-all) --> next --> 2-next --> create.

  * server creation:
    create 2-severs normal way.
     
